WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Cycling is great

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:05.500
It’s fun, fast, affordable, good for you and good for the environment

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:11.000
It’s also very safe too, providing you stick to a few common sense rules

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:18.500
Before you set out make sure your saddle isn’t set too high

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:27.000
A quick way to check this is to sit on the saddle and see if you can rest your feet on the ground

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:32.000
This is something you may need to do in emergency stopping situations
 
